- Thank you.

623
00:40:43,988 --> 00:40:45,216
Last one home's a rotten egg.

624
00:40:45,323 --> 00:40:46,950
No fair! You cheated!

625
00:40:47,058 --> 00:40:48,958
Wait!

626
00:40:49,727 --> 00:40:51,092
Hey!

627
00:40:52,830 --> 00:40:54,855
<i>Hey, wait up!</i>

628
00:40:56,100 --> 00:40:57,089
<i>"Dear Mother,</i>

629
00:40:57,201 --> 00:40:59,499
<i>You're never going to believe this,</i>

630
00:40:59,604 --> 00:41:02,004
<i>but today, under that giant tree,</i>

631
00:41:02,106 --> 00:41:05,564
<i>Mai actually met a ghost, Totoro.</i>

632
00:41:05,676 --> 00:41:08,008
<i>Daddy says
it was the king of the forest.</i>

633
00:41:08,112 --> 00:41:12,412
<i>Well, whoever he was,
I really want to meet him."</i>

634
00:41:20,925 --> 00:41:23,860
