00:42:05,303 --> 00:42:07,294
[Whispering]

639
00:42:07,405 --> 00:42:08,531
[Giggling]

640
00:42:19,817 --> 00:42:20,977
There.

641
00:42:24,021 --> 00:42:24,783
Huh?

642
00:42:29,660 --> 00:42:31,059
Mai? What. . .

643
00:42:31,162 --> 00:42:32,754
Excuse me.

644
00:42:32,864 --> 00:42:34,263
<i>Yes, Satsuki?</i>

645
00:42:34,365 --> 00:42:36,595
<i>I-i-it's my sister Mai.</i>

646
00:42:40,671 --> 00:42:42,901
<i>What's she going to do?</i>

647
00:42:43,007 --> 00:42:45,407
Nanny! Nanny, what happened?

648
00:42:45,509 --> 00:42:50,105
Dear, I'm sorry,
but she demanded to be with her sister.

649
00:42:50,448 --> 00:42:51,710
<i>But I'm going to be -</i>

650
00:42:51,816 --> 00:42:54,216
Mai, you promised to be a good girl

651
00:42:54,318 --> 00:42:58,186
<i>because Daddy's at the university
and can't take care of you.</i>

652
00:43:00,625 --> 00:43:02,684
<i>l have a couple hours left
before I can come home,</i>

653
00:43:02,793 --> 00:43:05,455
