654
00:43:05,563 --> 00:43:08,430
Our Mai has been a very good girl.

655
00:43:08,532 --> 00:43:09,521
Eh?

656
00:43:16,340 --> 00:43:20,436
Well, I better ask permission
for her to come inside.

657
00:43:26,250 --> 00:43:28,377
<i>Because her mother's going to be
in the hospital,</i>

658
00:43:28,486 --> 00:43:32,081
