669
00:44:04,322 --> 00:44:05,516
Come whenever you can.

670
00:44:05,623 --> 00:44:06,521
Bye, Mai.

671
00:44:06,624 --> 00:44:07,522
Goodbye.

672
00:44:08,092 --> 00:44:10,253
<i>We'd better walk fast,
