673
00:44:10,361 --> 00:44:11,658
O. K.

674
00:44:18,869 --> 00:44:20,837
Oh, no! Hurry!

675
00:44:28,846 --> 00:44:29,744
Oh!

676
00:44:30,281 --> 00:44:31,248
Oh, my god.

677
00:44:31,349 --> 00:44:32,748
Are you O. K.?

678
00:44:32,850 --> 00:44:33,441
Yeah.

679
00:44:33,551 --> 00:44:34,950
Come on.

680
00:44:42,727 --> 00:44:45,059
Wow. What do we do now?

681
00:44:47,298 --> 00:44:51,359
<i>lf it's not too much trouble,
could we stay until it stops raining?</i>

682
00:45:32,443 --> 00:45:33,307
Uh. . .

683
00:45:34,345 --> 00:45:36,176
Thanks.

684
00:45:36,680 --> 00:45:37,772
Uh. . .

685
00:45:46,190 --> 00:45:47,657
Ha ha.

686
00:45:49,026 --> 00:45:50,687
Whoo! Whoo-hoo!

687
00:45:56,133 --> 00:45:58,601
<i>We were pretty lucky, huh?</i>

688
00:45:59,203 --> 00:46:02,730
<i>Ha ha! That's funny.
