690
00:46:15,586 --> 00:46:17,383
Hey, we could bring it back to him.

691
00:46:20,424 --> 00:46:22,187
I just forgot because I forgot.

692
00:46:22,293 --> 00:46:24,227
How can you forget your umbrella

693
00:46:24,328 --> 00:46:25,226
<i>when it's raining?</i>

694
00:46:25,329 --> 00:46:27,957
<i>Even you can't be that stupid.</i>

695
00:46:28,065 --> 00:46:30,158
