696
00:46:30,267 --> 00:46:31,791
I did not!

697
00:46:37,441 --> 00:46:38,669
Hmm?

698
00:46:38,809 --> 00:46:40,674
Y-y-yii!

699
00:46:40,778 --> 00:46:41,938
[Crash]

700
00:46:44,682 --> 00:46:46,912
Excuse me. Is anybody home?

701
00:46:48,719 --> 00:46:50,778
<i>Satsuki, what are you doing here?</i>

702
00:46:50,888 --> 00:46:52,515
Grandma.

703
00:46:53,524 --> 00:46:55,082
Thank you for taking care of Mai.

704
00:46:55,192 --> 00:46:57,387
Don't be ridiculous.
She was a treasure.

705
00:46:57,495 --> 00:47:00,896
We wanted to bring back
the umbrella we borrowed.

706
00:47:00,998 --> 00:47:02,693
<i>But - Kanta's umbrella?</i>

707
00:47:02,800 --> 00:47:04,734
