this beat-up thing?

708
00:47:04,835 --> 00:47:09,295
<i>We didn't have one,
but I'm afraid he got soaking wet.</i>

709
00:47:09,406 --> 00:47:11,101
<i>Anyway, please thank him for us.</i>

710
00:47:11,208 --> 00:47:14,109
<i>l will.
I'm always telling him to wash,</i>

711
00:47:14,211 --> 00:47:16,111
