712
00:47:16,780 --> 00:47:18,771
Are you on your way to meet your father?

713
00:47:18,883 --> 00:47:19,611
<i>Yes, ma'am.</i>

714
00:47:19,717 --> 00:47:21,378
Give him my regards.

715
00:47:21,485 --> 00:47:23,350
- Bye-bye.
- Bye.

716
00:47:30,227 --> 00:47:31,660
Hee hee hee!

717
00:47:31,762 --> 00:47:33,787
[Imitating airplane]

718
00:47:33,898 --> 00:47:35,661
