720
00:47:40,738 --> 00:47:42,899
<i>Oh, boy, we made it!</i>

721
00:47:51,749 --> 00:47:52,909
Thank you.

722
00:47:53,717 --> 00:47:54,706
Thank you.

723
00:47:55,786 --> 00:47:57,413
