724
00:47:59,757 --> 00:48:01,418
<i>All right, let's go.</i>

725
00:48:08,766 --> 00:48:11,098
<i>Daddy wasn't on that one, right?</i>

726
00:48:11,202 --> 00:48:13,193
<i>I'm sure he'll be on the next one.</i>

727
00:48:13,304 --> 00:48:16,171
<i>Want to go back to Nanny's house
