00:48:51,308 --> 00:48:52,969
<i>What's the matter?</i>

730
00:49:24,608 --> 00:49:25,506
<i>Mai, you re sleepy.</i>

731
00:49:25,609 --> 00:49:26,268
Uh-uh.

732
00:49:26,377 --> 00:49:30,279
I told you it might be a while.

733
00:49:30,381 --> 00:49:32,906
<i>You don't want to go to Nanny's
and wait?</i>

734
00:49:34,585 --> 00:49:36,849
<i>I'm sure the bus will come soon.</i>

735
00:49:36,954 --> 00:49:38,979
Just hang in there.

736
00:49:42,259 --> 00:49:43,954
<i>Well, I guess they were delayed,</i>

737
00:49:44,061 --> 00:49:45,494
